column2: SELECT   m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,   n.objid, n.distance,   sp.ra AS ra2, sp.dec AS dec2,   sp.modelMag_r AS rmag,    sp.z AS redshift into MyDB.alfa_specz from MyDB.alfa_galaxies AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS sp ON n.objID = sp.specObjID WHERE sp.zWarning = #
